headline: How Can Qualcomm Stock Trade More Like Nvidia? Bring AI to Phones and Cars.
summary: The chip maker gets 75% of its revenue through smartphones, a big if mature market. To boost its multiple, Qualcomm has to convince investors that it can bring more AI to the devices through so-called edge computing. That’s a tough sell.
